headline: Centene (CNC) Faces Major Selloff, Mizuho Cuts Price Target Sharply to $40
summary: Centene Corp. (NYSE:CNC) is one of the most oversold S&P 500 stocks so far in 2025. On July 2, Centene’s share price plunged 40% after the company withdrew its 2025 earnings guidance. headline: CENTENE CORPORATION TO HOST 2025 SECOND QUARTER FINANCIAL RESULTS EARNINGS CALL
summary: Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC), a leading healthcare enterprise committed to helping people live healthier lives, announced today that it will release its 2025 second quarter financial results at approximately 6:00 a.m. ET on Friday, July 25, 2025, and host a conference call at 8:00 a.m. ET to review the results.
